channel.title: New Maps [PI]
channel.description: Well, I was looking around for some help on adding higher maps (508 to be specific), because I wanted things such as Godwars Dungeon and the Wilderness ditch, but once again, my cache is corrupted. I honestly have no clue how to work around this so I guess my question would be is there any way to add new maps even with a corrupted cache? :confused: :|
